{"tid":265981,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"細個對兄弟姊妹做過咩事令你一世都內疚","createTime":"2017-06-01T06:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T09:10:51.000Z","uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11f9097060b249b00fac80e8e9b8e820ed28d123","tid":265981,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T06:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發脾氣掟爛家姐啲野 碎曬一地都係<br />\n<br />\n大個諗返起果時佢喊個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32be07d5191a74863e415ce2db5b39a37e33f1d","tid":265981,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:04:33.000Z","msg":"十幾年前細個同細佬玩氣槍射中佢眼球，當年至到依家佢無講話有事，細個果時唔識諗，人大左覺得眼耳口鼻功能好重要，怕單野佢會有後遺症，好後悔。"},{"pid":"0b96cde4fd69f94399d72c3936a81e55aa6be46f","tid":265981,"uid":109889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:06:13.000Z","msg":"共同電腦個時霸哂部電腦<br />\n佢又冇手機 又唔鍾意睇書<br />\n都唔同個幾年係咁捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加斷絕左關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec6bcd58dab1e6016de104dadbc02f83b97ad36","tid":265981,"uid":109889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:07:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共同電腦個時霸哂部電腦<br />\n佢又冇手機 又唔鍾意睇書<br />\n都唔<span style=\"color: red;\">知</span>個幾年係<span style=\"color: red;\">點</span>捱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加斷絕左關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"421ef02623a17008eae1085814506788210e934a","tid":265981,"uid":93492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"笑佢矮，好彩宜家高過我"},{"pid":"6a8dda974037e2d60b07e11a49119ca47ccf2789","tid":265981,"uid":18110,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"細個篤灰家姐考第尾，佢比老母打到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4af33e56b6d259c31bacd0db0f0ce5e4ae06a4","tid":265981,"uid":34433,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:14:19.000Z","msg":"中學近DSE個期，有次放lunch返屋企食飯，家姐咁啱比人炒失業，兩個人嘈對方無做家務。嘈嘈下嘈到拍哂枱，好後悔講咗句 反正你都係係屋企'勾'架啦。<br />\n呀媽明我地自己既辛苦，勸交勸到半路喊咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對唔住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12064eb076639c8c7bf9d559a55c7100d3b1d2e","tid":265981,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:20:13.000Z","msg":"華人文化 兄弟姐妹都有競爭 諗番起好想嘔"},{"pid":"ef17e6cbfd0f018fb0b657ceb25c9686a7ae1418","tid":265981,"uid":1554,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"好多 細個好憎佢 會偷偷地打佢嗰啲 當佢唔識痛咁<br />\n而家好錫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73137344de65a8073d0aabd5d3f38273da27c2cb","tid":265981,"uid":47480,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:14:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多 細個好憎佢 會偷偷地打佢嗰啲 當佢唔識痛咁<br />\n而家好錫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗返起打爛人地野果陣 未必買得返/好有記諗價值 就覺得自己好賤"},{"pid":"eba480d846c058e4701b2bc4fccc81b9744f8f83","tid":265981,"uid":90352,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T12:44:51.000Z","msg":"一拳打到阿哥訓係地下"},{"pid":"b2413480ee211262c73061790785fc794c7de1bf","tid":265981,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一拳打到阿哥訓係地下</blockquote><br />\n最後你比佢打到仆街"},{"pid":"90daa99443f6f72d4cf9c812bb437e0306372da4","tid":265981,"uid":75452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"